Name: Jumping Jax
About the game: Jax is your teleporting cyborg corgi. A Cyborgi, if you will. Jax wants to play. To him, that means teleporting around the city while you chase after him! You'll have to use interesting movement mechanics (bunny-hopping, portals, bounce-pads and more!) to bring Jax home before dinner. Cyborgis still need their exercise - take Jax for a walk with the help of the Steam Workshop!
